1) Users can explore and browse for posters

2) Users can click on a poster to transmitted to another page to see the full details of that poster

3) In poster show page, users can type a text, select a font, select a color, and request similar poster with selected specification

4) the artist (owner) can add poster along with its specification(font, color, category ...)

5) artist(owner) dashboard will display a list of all posters requests and their specification (user name, phone number,selected features ...ext)


Database:

Sign:
    id
    Name
    image
    rate
    color
    prodate
    featured
    description

request:
    id
    username
    phone
    email
    sign